one of the ones that we intended right from the start

13
00:00:33,105 --> 00:00:35,766
was finding a voice for your hero through visual effects.

14
00:00:36,326 --> 00:00:38,788
and really telling their story and making them unique.

15
00:00:38,788 --> 00:00:40,649
An explosive new Spider-Man.

16
00:00:40,649 --> 00:00:43,350
So an explosive new Spider-Man was one of the pillars

