00:00:43,350 --> 00:00:45,191
of this game and it's something that the effects team

18
00:00:45,191 --> 00:00:46,912
really glommed onto.

19
00:00:46,912 --> 00:00:51,015
We found a lot of fun in making Miles our own hero

20
00:00:51,015 --> 00:00:54,617
and finding ways to differentiate him from the hero

